        {"input": "Turn 1: I have two siblings, a brother and a sister. ... Turn 5: How many siblings do I have?", "expected": "Two", "rubric": "Model must recall specific relational data."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: The secret word is 'Banana'. ... Turn 8: What was the secret word?", "expected": "Banana", "rubric": "Model must recall arbitrary data points explicitly assigned."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: Assume the gravity on this planet is 5 m/s^2. ... Turn 4: Calculate the fall time for an object dropped from 10m.", "expected": "2 seconds", "rubric": "Model must use custom physics parameters defined earlier (t = sqrt(2d/g))."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: My budget is $500. ... Turn 5: Suggest a laptop for me to buy.", "expected": "Laptop under $500", "rubric": "Model must recall numeric constraints."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: I am writing a story about a knight named Sir Reginald. ... Turn 6: Describe the main character's armor.", "expected": "Armor for Sir Reginald (a knight)", "rubric": "Model must maintain narrative consistency with established characters."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: Set the timezone to JST. ... Turn 4: What time is it if it's 12:00 UTC?", "expected": "21:00", "rubric": "Model must remember setting configurations across turns."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: I'm speaking to you from Mars. ... Turn 5: How long does a year last where I am?", "expected": "687 Earth days", "rubric": "Model must infer answers based on previously established roleplay/setting."},
        {"input": "Turn 1: First item is eggs. Turn 2: Second item is milk. ... Turn 5: What is on my list?", "expected": "Eggs and milk", "rubric": "Model must aggregate state built up over multiple turns."},
